<hr>
<p>If you want to help with it, you need to be a developer:</p>
<ul>
<li>Knowledge of bash shell scripting and some sysadmin skills for lack of better term. That means skill to figure out how to use tools which are required for such a process such as xorriso, grub, isolinux, etc. Saying “skill to figure out” because I doubt anyone is born with this skills or already has them and now is interested to contribute.</li>
<li>There is already <code>--target iso</code>.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/derivative-maker/derivative-maker/blob/master/build-steps.d/2550_convert-raw-to-iso" class="inline-onebox">derivative-maker/2550_convert-raw-to-iso at master · derivative-maker/derivative-maker · GitHub</a></li>
</ul>
