        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Yes, check out <a href="https://github.com/Whonix/derivative-maker">https://github.com/Whonix/derivative-maker</a>. Make Kicksecure ISO building functional (easier). Or go straight to Whonix ISO building. Send git branches or pull requests. Once that’s working, support for both, BIOS and EFI booting would be nice.</p>
